[07:58:07.861] [INFO ]   Q: What are NovaAI's primary market verticals?
[07:58:07.861] [INFO ] ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
