[08:03:47.863] [INFO ]   Q: How does NovaAI's performance review cycle work?
[08:03:47.863] [INFO ] ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
