[14:26:27.076] [INFO ]     NovaAI offers a 401(k) match of **100% on up to 4% of your eligible compensation**. This means if you contribute 4% of your salary, NovaAI contributes an additional 4%; if you contribute less, the company matches dollar-for-dollar up to that 4% cap.
    
    **Eligibility**: Employees are eligible to participate in the 401(k) plan **30 days after their hire date**. There is no separate waiting period for the match—you can start receiving it as soon as you enroll and begin contributing.
    
    **Additional Details**:
    - **Vesting**: The employer match vests immediately (100% vested from day one).
    - **Plan Provider**: Fidelity Investments
    - **Auto-enrollment**: New hires are automatically enrolled at a 3% contribution rate with a 1% annual auto-escalation feature (up to 10%).
    - **Roth Option**: Both traditional pre-tax and Roth 401(k) contributions are available.
    
    If you need the most current plan documents or have questions about specific scenarios, contact the HR Benefits team or log into the Fidelity portal via your NovaAI employee dashboard.
